  "audioUrl": "/narration.mp3",
  "duration": 0,
  "phrases": [
    {
      "text": "Hi,",
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 0.36
    },
    {
      "text": "I'm Xander.",
      "start": 0.72,
      "end": 1.1
    },
    {
      "text": "I build software,",
      "start": 1.94,
      "end": 2.8
    },
    {
      "text": "make music,",
      "start": 3.04,
      "end": 3.5
    },
    {
      "text": "and hike around Lake Tahoe.",
      "start": 3.74,
      "end": 4.92
    },
    {
      "text": "I study software engineering and music technology at Chapman University.",
      "start": 5.42,
      "end": 9.48
    },
    {
      "text": "Last summer,",
      "start": 10.44,
      "end": 11.24
    },
    {
      "text": "I was in San Francisco.",
      "start": 11.42,
      "end": 12.3
    },
    {
      "text": "Sitting outside a restaurant,",
      "start": 13.26,
      "end": 14.46
    },
    {
      "text": "a guy approached me from the sidewalk.",
      "start": 14.8,
      "end": 16.38
    },
    {
      "text": "He was a founder making AI generated floor plans to build houses.",
      "start": 17.14,
      "end": 20.96
    },
    {
      "text": "I thought his idea was really cool,",
      "start": 21.64,
      "end": 23.56
    },
    {
      "text": "so I asked him for his website.",
      "start": 23.56,
      "end": 25.06
    },
    {
      "text": "He didn't have one,",
      "start": 25.82,
      "end": 26.68
    },
    {
      "text": "so I went to the Founder's Inc office and built it!",
      "start": 27.12,
      "end": 29.54
    },
    {
      "text": "I sent him a website two hours after meeting him.",
      "start": 30.36,
      "end": 33.18
    },
    {
      "text": "That brief interaction turned into working together.",
      "start": 33.9,
      "end": 36.38
    },
    {
      "text": "I built their MVP doing full stack web development.",
      "start": 37.16,
      "end": 40.56
    },
    {
      "text": "I think about software the way Rick Rubin thinks about music.",
      "start": 41.54,
      "end": 44.86
    },
    {
      "text": "There are a lot of producers,",
      "start": 45.68,
      "end": 46.98
    },
    {
      "text": "but not enough reducers.",
      "start": 47.46,
      "end": 48.86
    },
    {
      "text": "I strip things down until only the part that matters is left.",
      "start": 49.74,
      "end": 52.94
    },
    {
      "text": "I do that with code,",
      "start": 53.66,
      "end": 54.66
    },
    {
      "text": "design,",
      "start": 55.04,
      "end": 55.48
    },
    {
      "text": "and music.",
      "start": 55.9,
      "end": 56.34
    },
    {
      "text": "I like to work sustainably.",
      "start": 57.26,
      "end": 58.7
    },
    {
      "text": "I learned that ambition is purely the size of the outcome.",
      "start": 59.38,
      "end": 62.38
    },
    {
      "text": "It has nothing to do with how much you sacrifice yourself to reach it.",
      "start": 63.04,
      "end": 66.56
    },
    {
      "text": "Last winter,",
      "start": 67.18,
      "end": 67.82
    },
    {
      "text": "I worked as a ski instructor.",
      "start": 68.24,
      "end": 69.68
    },
    {
      "text": "I loved being outside,",
      "start": 70.34,
      "end": 71.78
    },
    {
      "text": "moving around,",
      "start": 72.36,
      "end": 73.08
    },
    {
      "text": "and teaching people something new.",
      "start": 73.44,
      "end": 74.84
    },
    {
      "text": "And right now,",
      "start": 75.5,
      "end": 76.42
    },
    {
      "text": "I'm building a project called Stoodious.",
      "start": 76.88,
      "end": 78.66
    },
    {
      "text": "It helps students turn their degree audits into four-year plans that actually make sense.",
      "start": 79.26,
      "end": 83.92
    },
    {
      "text": "This summer,",
      "start": 84.72,
      "end": 85.68
    },
    {
      "text": "I'm looking for a team to build with.",
      "start": 85.94,
      "end": 87.62
    },
    {
      "text": "If that's you,",
      "start": 88.0,
      "end": 88.72
    },
    {
      "text": "please reach out!",
      "start": 89.04,
      "end": 89.8
    }
  ]
}
